Template: emperor/dbhost
Type: string
Default: localhost
Description: Database host
 What host will your database be running?

Template: emperor/dbname
Type: string
Default: emperor
Description: Database name
 What is the name of the database?

Template: emperor/dbuser
Type: string
Default: emperor
Description: Databaser username
 What is the username to use for connecting to the database?

Template: emperor/dbpass
Type: string
Description: Databaser password
 What is the password to use for connecting to the database?